headline: Iranian Officials Expect  To Announce the Cause Of a Jet Crash Today
abstract: The announcement comes as American and allied intelligence assessments have suggested that Iranian missiles brought down the plane, most likely by accident.
lead_paragraph: Iranian officials plan to meet with international investigators on Saturday and announce the cause of the Ukrainian jetliner crash near Tehran this week that killed all 176 aboard, Iranâ€™s semiofficial Fars News Agency reported on Friday, capping a day of international recriminations.
